title: The First Years Stack N Count Cups
description: When building baby's toy collection, start with these classic Toys! Nesting stacking cups are popular for a reason, offering simple-yet-fun ways to play. Children love to fit toy cups together, stack them up, or turn them over and hide things underneath. These eight colorful cup toys for baby have large numbers embossed on the base so an older child can practice counting and begin building number recognition skills. You can "count" on hours of fun with these toy cups!
